title: Big Ego Accountability
itunes:title: Big Ego Accountability
description:
Today on the show we took Kanye West to Breakfast Club Court, after his recent rants and post about Pete Davidson, his ex-wife Kim and his kids, DL Hughley and our very own Charlamagne tha God. Moreover, Charlagmagne even decides to give Kanye "Donkey of the Day" for his irrational reactions towards Kim moving on to Pete Davidson and his kids being on Tik Tok, with the main message of letting go ego. Also, we speak with the creator of Telfar on genderless clothing, connecting with Solange, building the brand and more.
